main event: A 2nd Lieutenant reported observing three unidentified objects in Lakeland, Florida on November 7, 1955.
interesting points: The observation lasted 15 minutes at 2315Z,Objects were likely associated with a B-47 aircraft in the area at the time,This report corroborates previous sightings in the region during reconnaissance flights,The lieutenant noted that visual contact with the objects was intermittently lost and regained,The report was sent to various defense and intelligence commands for further analysis.
